类 Map

java.lang.Object
Map
public class Map extends Object
This class holds the map to search for a path in. A map is a set of nodes connected by links.

      Singleton class.

    • getNodes

      Returns the nodes in this map.
      返回:

    • setLinkAsVisited

      public void setLinkAsVisited​(Node n)
      Shows the link as visited in the GUI. The link is the one connecting the specified node and its parent.
      参数:
      n - The node

    • getLinks

      public Vector<Link> getLinks()
      Returns the links in this map.
      返回:
      A list of links

    • resetLinks

      public void resetLinks()
      Resets all links from being shown.

    • reset

      public void reset()
      Resets a map. This removes the path from being shown in the GUI and clears all parent references for nodes.

    • load

      public void load​(String mapID)
      Loads a map.
      参数:
      mapID - The map to load

    • reload

      public void reload()
      Reloads the current map.

    • readMap

      public void readMap()
      Reads a new map.

    • parseLine

      public void parseLine​(String line)
      Parses a line read from a map file. 逐行处理数据，生成地图（节点、连接线、开始结束位置）
      参数:
      line - The line to parse

    • dumpMap

      public void dumpMap()
      Dumps the map to code. Used when creating new maps in the GUI.

    • getNewNodeLabel

      public String getNewNodeLabel()
      Creates a new unique label (increasing integer number) used for new nodes.
      返回:
      The new unique label

    • removeNode

      public boolean removeNode​(String label)
      Removes a node from the map. Used by the GUI when the user changes the map.
      参数:
      label - The label of the node to remove
      返回:
      True if the node was successfully removed, falst otherwise

    • addNode

      public boolean addNode​(int x, int y, String label)
      Adds a new node to the map. Used by the GUI when the user changes the map.
      参数:
      x - X-coordinate
      y - Y-coordinate
      label - Label for the node
      返回:
      True if the node was successfully added, false otherwise

    • addLink

      public boolean addLink​(String node1, String node2)
      Adds a new link between two nodes. Used by the GUI when the user changes the map.
      参数:
      node1 - First node
      node2 - Second node
      返回:
      True if the link was successfully added, false otherwise

    • removeLink

      public boolean removeLink​(String label)
      Removes a link from the map. Used by the GUI when the user changes the map.
      参数:
      label - The label of the link to remove
      返回:
      True if the link was successfully removed, false otherwise

    • findLink

      public Link findLink​(String label)
      Finds the link with the specified label.
      参数:
      label - The label of the link
      返回:
      The link, or null if not found

      Returns the start node in the map.
      返回:
      The start node

    • setAsStartNode

      public void setAsStartNode​(String label)
      Changes the start node in the map. Used by the GUI when the user changes the map.
      参数:
      label - The label of the new start node

    • getEndNode

      public Node getEndNode()
      Returns the end node in the map.
      返回:
      The end node

    • setAsEndNode

      public void setAsEndNode​(String label)
      Changes the end node in the map. Used by the GUI when the user changes the map.
      参数:
      label - The end of the new start node

    • getLink

      public Link getLink​(Node a, Node b)
      Returns the link between two nodes.
      参数:
      a - First node
      b - Second node
      返回:
      The link between the nodes, or null if no link was found
